    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "6. Un Dahwids likke Karra-\nWihrus eekſch Damaskus Sih-\nrexn Seimē. Un tee Sihrexi\ntappe Dahwidam par Kalveem\nDahwanas nesdami / nn tas\nKUNGS palihdſeja Dahwidam\nwiſſur/ korp wiſſch gabje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Un Dahwids nehme tahs\npreeſchturrainas Selta Brux-\nnas / kas Adad-Esefxa Kalveem\nbija / un neffe tohs uhs Jeru-\nsalemi-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Tas Kehniſsch Dahwids\nnehme arridsan dands Warra no\nBetas un Berotajas Adad-Ee-\nfera Pilſſahteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Kad nu Tojus tas Keh-\nniſch no Eematas dsirdeja / ka\nDahwids wiſſu Karra-Spehku\nAdad-Esefa bij kawis/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Tad fuhtiſa Tojus fawu\nDehlu Joramu pee to Kehniſzu-\nDahwidu/ pehz wiſſa Labklab-\nſchanas waizaht/ un wiſſam pa-\nteikt par to / ka wiſſch prett A-\ndad-Eesern bij karrojs / un wiſ-\nnu bij kawis / ( jo Tojum bija\nKarſch ar Adad-Eseru). Un\nwiſſch neffe arfew lihds Sudraba\nun Selta un Warra Ribkus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Ir tohs jwehtiſa tas Keh-\nniſch Dahwidſtam KUNgam/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "12. No Sihrijas/ un no Mo-\naba / un no Ammona Behr-\nneem/ un no teem Wilistereem\nun no teem Amalekitereem/ no ta\nLaupijuma Adad-Eesera/ ta Deh-\nla Rekaba/ ta kehnixa no Jobas\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "13. Dahwids darrijaſs fe-\narridsan angstu Slavu / ka-\nwisch atgreeſehß/ kad wiſſch\nSahls-Eeleija astonpadefiniti-\ntuhkſtochus Sihreus bij kawis\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "14. Un wiſſch likke Karra-\nWihrus Gedoma/ wiſſu Eedo-\nmā likke wiſſch Karra-Wihrus\nun wiſſi Eedomiteri tappe Dah-\nwidam par Kalveem/ un ta-\nKUNGS palihdſeja Dahwidam\nwiſſur/ korp tas gabje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Ta walduja Dahwid-\npahr wiſſu Israēlu/ un Dahwid-\nneffe wiſſeem Landim Teefu u-\nTaifnibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Un Joabs Zerujaē Dehſ-\nbija pahr to Karra-Spehku / u-\nJosavats Akiluda Dehſs bij-\nRanzleris.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Un Zadaks Akitaba Dehts-\nun Akimeleks Abjatara Dehl-\nbija Preestert/ un Serajus bij-\nRaſſitajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Un Benajus Jojad-\nDehſs bija pahr teem Kreeti u-\nVleeti / bet Dahwida Dehſi bij-\nLeeli-Kungi.\n"
    }
